This module is demo.lambdamatchbind.

Define User with id: Text, name: Text.


To greetUser with u: User and pfx: Text, produce Text:
  Let f be function with x: User, produce Text:
    Match x:
      When User(id, name), Return Text.concat(pfx, name).
  Return f(u).


To posOrZero with n: Int, produce Int:
  Let sel be function with x: Int, produce Int:
    If x < 0,:
      Return 0.
    Otherwise,:
      Return x.
  Return sel(n).
